data.value: Waverley Streeet,Nottingham,Nottinghamshire,NG7 4GH House | 4 Bed The Arboretum is a popular area of Nottingham, situated approximately a mile to the north of the city centre. It hosts a variety of different property types, mainly period terrace houses but larger properties can also be found along it streets. The area is serviced by a variety of local shops and business as well as well-known outlets. The city is easily accessed on any number of main bus routes that pass through the area. The High School Tram Stop is situated just opposite. It is located ideally between both hospital campuses and good links to the M1 Motorway Junction 26.
